Title: Dynamical systems accepting the normal shift on an arbitrary Riemannian
  manifold
Authors: A. Yu. Boldin, V. V. Dmitrieva, S. S. Safin, R. A. Sharipov (Bashkir
  State University)
Comments: 10 pages. Published in book: "Dynamical systems accepting the normal
  shift". Editor Sharipov R.A., Bashkir State University, Ufa 1994, pp. 4-19
Subj-class: High Energy Physics - Theory; Differential Geometry; Chaotic
  Dynamics
Journal-ref: Theor.Math.Phys. 103 (1995) 543-549; Teor.Mat.Fiz. 103N2 (1995)
  256-266
\\
  Newtonian dynamical systems which accept the normal shift on an arbitrary
Riemannian manifold are considered. For them the determinating equations making
the weak normality condition are derived. The expansion for the algebra of
tensor fields is constructed.
